  "texts": [
    "(iii) economic barriers concerning the feasibility and actual costs and damages related to data sharing and potential solutions hinge on acknowledging the value of data and implementing sustainable financing mechanisms.",
    "(iv) political barriers ingrained within health governance systems often manifest as issues related to trust, restrictive policies, and lack of guidelines.",
    "Addressing them is not a clear-cut endeavor, requiring national and global processes to foster agreement and political will.",
    "(v) legal barriers related to ownership, copyrights, and privacy protection.",
    "Resolving them relies on underlying political barriers."
  ]
}